Why would you use class component over function components (removing hooks from the question)?
 
I would need a class component to utilize state and pass it down to child components.

 Name three lifecycle methods and their purposes.

1.Render : Render handles the rendering of your component to your UI 
2.componentDidMount : componentDidMount is used commonly to make API calls when the component is mounted 
3.componentDidUpdate : used to make changes to the dom after the change of props or state


